dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Brian Edwards. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Judy. Can you provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five six seven eight nine and my date of birth is zero six dash one seven dash one nine eight zero.
Thank you, Judy. I have verified your information. Can you also confirm the make and model of your vehicle for our records?
Of course, my vehicle is a two zero one five Toyota Camry.
Thank you for providing that information, Judy. Is there anything specific you would like to inquire about or update regarding your policy today?
I would like to add a new driver to my policy, my husband John Moore.
Certainly, Judy. I will assist you with adding John Moore as a driver. Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
No, that will be all. Thank you for your help, Brian.
You're welcome, Judy. Have a great day and feel free to contact us anytime. Goodbye.
